he on exit interface</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.IOnFixedUpdate.html'>IOnFixedUpdate</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The on fixed update interface</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.IOnHoldKey.html'>IOnHoldKey</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Interfaz para gestionar el evento de mantener pulsada una tecla</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.IOnInit.html'>IOnInit</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The initable interface</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.IOnPhysicUpdate.html'>IOnPhysicUpdate</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The on physic update interface</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.IOnPressKey.html'>IOnPressKey</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The on press key interface</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.IOnProcessPendingChanges.html'>IOnProcessPendingChanges</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The on process pending changes interface</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.IOnReleaseKey.html'>IOnReleaseKey</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Interfaz para gestionar el evento de soltar una tecla</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.IOnStart.html'>IOnStart</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Fluent.Components.yml\" sourceStartLi